Hey friends!  What a season it's been - This Adventure of Blink is flying right by.  We have a working game, but... we'd like to have a little something more.  What if we had special bricks in the game that, when you hit them, caused a second ball to enter the game?

Stop by the channel and let's build together... and please leave me a 👍🏻, a 💬, and subscribe!

